Titolo: Chess 2: The Sequel

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Chess 2: The Sequel is a chess variant created by David Sirlin and Zachary Burns of Ludeme Games. Sirlin, whose previous design work includes rebalancing Super Street Fighter II Turbo HD Remix, approached what he believed to be a problem of rote endgames and static opening games in chess by introducing asymmetrical piece compositions and an additional win condition. A video game version of Chess 2 is available on Ouya as of 2014.
The game was released on Steam on 19 August 2014.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
